    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 id="roi-heading">What changes when AI runs the daily grind</h2>
      <p>Toggle to compare a typical UAE retailer's day before and after deploying Aegis AI systems.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="roi-toggle-wrap">
      <input type="checkbox" id="roi-toggle" class="roi-toggle-input" />
      <label for="roi-toggle" class="roi-toggle-label">
        <span class="roi-toggle-option roi-toggle-before">Manual operations</span>
        <span class="roi-toggle-track"><span class="roi-toggle-thumb"></span></span>
        <span class="roi-toggle-option roi-toggle-after">With Aegis AI</span>
      </label>
